description: Try our easy to follow Cherry Compote recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Compote & coulis,Cherry,Low saturated fat,Low salt,Christmas,Low fat
name: Cherry Compote Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a medium saucepan over medium heat. When hot, add onion and cook for 4 minutes or until soft. Stir in garam masala and nutmeg. Cook for 1 minute. Add cherries, sugar, port and sage. Stir until sugar dissolves and mixture comes to the boil. Simmer for 10 minutes or until mixture thickens. Remove from heat and allow to cool.
Pour compote into a large sterilised jar and seal. Refrigerate for up to 2 months. Serve with turkey, ham, chicken or lamb.
